Package: smartpkg
Title: Smart R Package Installer with Automatic Fastest Mirror Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "your@email.com")
Description: Provides a unified smart_install() function that replaces
    install.packages(), BiocManager::install(), and remotes::install_github().
    Automatically detects the fastest CRAN mirror using two-step probing
    (concurrent HEAD requests + real download verification), caches results
    for 24 hours, and intelligently routes package sources to the correct
    installation backend.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Imports:
    utils
Suggests:
    curl,
    BiocManager,
    remotes,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
NeedsCompilation: no
